<img srcset="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/uMdqxnYi_ySpl2Q48PfBMt9qxPo=/0x0:2040x1360/320x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19901209/cwelch_200414_3974_0004.jpg 320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7pZYbVoTWTjHqDfu1x8MaWo41iA=/0x0:2040x1360/520x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19901209/cwelch_200414_3974_0004.jpg 520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/GuR69hGbuL_YsqV7hgzBy--alyM=/0x0:2040x1360/720x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19901209/cwelch_200414_3974_0004.jpg 720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/WHC6TKv7RIoLiREKPKN68bKR4vI=/0x0:2040x1360/920x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19901209/cwelch_200414_3974_0004.jpg 920w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ffunGHOc7P-wyVVWCJmWZKCkVUs=/0x0:2040x1360/1120x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19901209/cwelch_200414_3974_0004.jpg 1120w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/TBKlLQco9uxQUir1Fbt1xdK4IH8=/0x0:2040x1360/1320x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19901209/cwelch_200414_3974_0004.jpg 1320w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/szT7V0nB7z5JqHDoJVRpQb4Nx-Y=/0x0:2040x1360/1520x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19901209/cwelch_200414_3974_0004.jpg 1520w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0rAkBQjpfZjVRpZSLwhB3DlNyM8=/0x0:2040x1360/1720x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19901209/cwelch_200414_3974_0004.jpg 1720w, https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/4B-xKWIu-TCEMCT3V910OJtBRe8=/0x0:2040x1360/1920x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19901209/cwelch_200414_3974_0004.jpg 1920w" sizes="(min-width: 1221px) 846px, (min-width: 880px) calc(100vw - 334px), 100vw" alt="" data-upload-width="2040" src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/6q4PCw6oGjz18Xjo58JX3mvaPSE=/0x0:2040x1360/1200x0/filters:focal(0x0:2040x1360):no_upscale()/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/19901209/cwelch_200414_3974_0004.jpg">

</source></picture>

      
    </span>
    
  </span>
  
</figure>

</div>
</div></div>
<p id="8asC5x">You can always count on LG to toss in one very strange camera feature, and this time, it’s 3D photos. If you’ve ever seen one of these on Facebook, you know what to expect. You snap a shot, and the V60 uses depth information to create the illusion that the focused-on object is shifting around as you move your phone. I took like two of these and then ignored 3D photos altogether. A nicer, more important touch about the camera is that, in most lighting conditions, the viewfinder is displayed at 60fps. It doesn’t really add any benefit, but now that I’ve had a taste, I want that smoothness from the camera on every other phone. </p>
<div id="ljTLXz">
